direction right
colorMode bold
styleMode plain
typeface clean

Detect [label: "1. Detect\nCloudWatch Alarm", icon: aws-cloudwatch, color: red]
Reason [label: "2. Reason\nLambda + Bedrock", icon: aws-bedrock, color: blue]
Remediate [label: "3. Remediate\nStep Functions + ASG", icon: aws-step-functions, color: green]
VerifyLearn [label: "4. Verify + Learn\nLambda + DynamoDB/S3", icon: aws-dynamodb, color: purple]

Incident [label: "Incident Payload", icon: aws-eventbridge, color: orange, colorMode: outline]
Telemetry [label: "Telemetry\nCloudWatch + ASG + CloudTrail", icon: aws-cloudwatch, color: blue, colorMode: outline]
Knowledge [label: "Knowledge Base\nS3 Runbooks + DynamoDB History", icon: aws-s3, color: purple, colorMode: outline]
Policy [label: "Policy\nSystem Prompt + Allowed Actions", icon: aws-lambda, color: gray, colorMode: outline]
TrustBoundary [label: "Bedrock recommends. Lambda validates. Step Functions executes.", color: gray, colorMode: outline]

Detect > Reason: Alarm
Reason > Remediate: Approved action
Remediate > VerifyLearn: Recovery result

Incident > Reason
